EnumField[NNode] = object
  docComment*: string
  codeComment*: string
  name*: string
  value*: Option[NNode]
  declNode*: Option[NNode]
  case kind*: EnumFieldVal
  of efvNone:
      nil

  of efvIdent:
      ident*: NNode

  of efvOrdinal:
      ordVal*: RTimeOrdinal

  of efvString:
      strval*: string

  of efvOrdString:
      ordStr*: tuple[ordVal: RTimeOrdinal, strval: string]

    ImplementKindError, ArgumentError, UnexpectedKindError], tags: [].}
